				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/B%C3%A1t-tu%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-Yw7Ol_bL1s3AlGhfEnPyrw">Bát tuấn đồ - 八駿圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/B%C3%ACnh-Ng%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-c%C3%A1o/poem-mLEGY5d9nFI0RH280X-vIQ">Bình Ngô đại cáo - 平吳大告</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-DAnV8dGIPFm4CWSv9BPBcQ">Hữu cảm kỳ 3 - 有感其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Qu%C3%BD-Ly/K%C3%BD-Nguy%C3%AAn-Qu%C3%A2n/poem-Pj2gpsH_WQUnW0mwktBXmg">Ký Nguyên Quân - 寄元君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Qu%C3%BD-Ly/author-7nvHkfkxqjn6llEbexL2og">Hồ Quý Ly</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Huy%E1%BB%81n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Nh%C3%A2n-s%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-C%E1%BB%A9u-Lan-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-s1Ff_-O4VXchhvZ6XQAX1g">Nhân sự đề Cứu Lan tự - 因事題究蘭寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Huy%E1%BB%81n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-ky6a-6Hq9AEiujrHK0DNTQ">Huyền Quang thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/Nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%B1-B%E1%BA%AFc-Ninh-lai-ng%C3%B4n-B%E1%BA%AFc-Ninh-s%E1%BB%B1-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-CFGlXtKzg-7M-QcXEABMCw">Nhân tự Bắc Ninh lai, ngôn Bắc Ninh sự cảm tác - 人自北寧來言北寧事感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/Qu%C3%